These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, hedgehog, mouse
1. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the mouse##7
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Pet   | hedgehog | ferret | mouse | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, pineapple, banana, grapes
1. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the person eating banana is somewhere between the person eating pineapple and the person eating onion##7
3. the person eating banana is between the person eating pineapple and the person eating grapes##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | onion | grapes | banana | pineapple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, avocado, lettuce, apricot
1. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
2. the person eating apricot is somewhere between the person eating lettuce and the person eating avocado##7
3. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the person eating apricot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |  2   |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | tomato | avocado | apricot | lettuce |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, motorbike, scooter, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the motorbike##7
2. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person driving the car is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the scooter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Transport   | scooter | car | quad-bike | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, satire, romance, musical
1. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching musical movies##2
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
4. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching romance movies and the person watching musical movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | scientific | satire | musical |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, egyptian, dutch, japanese
1. the malaysian is somewhere between the japanese and the egyptian##7
2. the dutch is somewhere between the malaysian and the japanese##7
3. the dutch is on the left or right of the japanese##3
4. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| Nationality   | japanese | dutch | malaysian | egyptian |

