2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking coffee##7
3. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2     |   3   |      4      |
| Beverage   | cola | mirinda | hot-chocolate | coffee |

